{
  "stem": "24397.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we, we enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I, I, I guess because of that, I still enjoy listening to the music this time of the year.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't look upon it in threatening in any way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have good memories from that period.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, 10 to, to 14, I was there all that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In England?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, I hate to chastise the whole British population based on the couple that I stayed with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This person didn't have a clue of cooking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I would find things like a pig's ear with hair still on it on a plate in front of me and expected to eat that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to spit things into my handkerchief and, and let it out on the street as I took the dog for a walk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She only knew one thing-- you boil everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think, I mean, England is not known for its kind of cooking anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this was, this was rock bottom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was only her husband and my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister somehow used to swallow things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'd see her face peering at me because she knew what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but that's, that's the way I survived there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I used to-- at the farm, I used to have milk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to have cheese there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And vegetables I could always manage anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the food there was pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, first of all, at this time, you know, it wasn't long-- I don't know how long it took for me to grasp the language and speak it with the same London accent as the others but really not long at all.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't practice any Jewish holidays while I was in that.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
